      <scopecontent id="aspace_f1a806c30a07815797efb51e2b02b81e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consists of correspondence, pedigree and registration, a scrapbook, and printed material documenting the lives of Handsome Dan XII, XIII and XV. Included are letters by Christopher Getman, keeper of Handsome Dan, the Yale mascot.</p>  
